*** NO EPISODES OF AFTER DARK HAVE BEEN MISSED! ***

The live feeds were cut prior to the Nomination Ceremony on Saturday and not restarted until after the Sunday night show. As a result After Dark did not air on Sunday morning.For future reference I always try to leave a comment on the previous episode when something like this is happening so that you don't have to speculate why an episode is not being posted.
